title: Tribute to a Bad Man
description:
Jeremy Rodock is a tough horse rancher who strings up rustlers soon as look at them. Fresh out of Pennsylvania, Steve Miller finds it hard to get used to Rodock&#039;s ways, although he takes an immediate shine to his Greek girl Jocasta.
